Detailed Description

The ROS control implementation of the Cartesian impedance controller.

It utilizes a list of joint names and the URDF description to control these joints.

If the wrench is not given in end-effector frame, it will be transformed in the root frame. Once when a new wrench message arrives. Sets the wrench using the base library.

See also
applyWrench.
